description:
A grouping that allows brokers to share a combination of documents, contracts and sections with underwriters.

If querying of unique submission is desired the following achieves this:

```json
[{
   $match: {
      access: {
         $in: [<userID>]
      },
      "sections.participations.sent": true
   }
   }, {
   $group: {
      _id: "sections.participations.submission_date",
      recipients: { 
         $addToSet: "$sections.participations" 
     }
   }
   }
]
```

